# Evidence – Phishing Detection & Awareness

This folder contains supporting material used for **Task 2: Phishing Detection & Awareness**, completed as part ofthe **Cyber Security Internship Program at Future Interns**.

The evidence included here supports the analysis and findings documented in the phishing awareness report.

---

## 📧 Evidence Description

The evidence in this folder may include:

- Sample phishing email content used for analysis  
- Screenshots showing suspicious links or domains  
- Safe inspection of URLs and domains using browser tools  
- Any reference material used to explain phishing indicators  

All samples were handled in a **read-only and non-interactive manner**.

---

## 🛠️ Tools Used for Evidence Collection
- Public phishing email samples (provided in task description)
- Browser tools (for safe inspection of links and domains)
- Email header analysis tools (study/reference only)

---

## ⚠️ Ethical Notice
- No real user accounts were used  
- No malicious links were clicked  
- No emails were sent or interacted with  
- All analysis was performed strictly for **educational and awareness purposes**

